room_title: Escape room "Superhero Training Facility" by Mastermind Escape Games in Atlanta
room_address: 5825 Glenridge Dr Building 4 Suite #200, Atlanta, GA 30328
room_description: You can't wait to join the Superhero squad and dedicate yourself to protecting civilians, but first, you have to pass the final exam. Choose a superpower and test your strength, intelligence and skill at a three-part obstacle course. And if that sounds easy, keep in mind: you only have 60 minutes.
